name: Sister Ruth
description:
3840x2796 | 60fps | High@L6 x264avc | 14mb bit rate | YUV 4:2:0 | 8 bit

“Yes, she's a problem. I'm afraid she'll be a problem for you, too. With a smaller community, she may be better. Give her responsibility, Sister. She badly wants importance.” -Mother Dorothea

Originally captured from a second of the film 'Black Narcissus' when Sister Ruth has freed herself from repression and gone mad.  Processed through some light glitchy algorithms and upscaled to 4k with some light sharpening and grain added.  Multiple variations of glitchiness exists and I may post a series of them as just 640p gifs. Video may not play smoothly in browser.
